title: Jinx with 4 Infinity Edges (A Long Time Ago)

embed.description: READ DESCRIPTION!!!! This is me playing some Jinx in Team Builder. So I decided on building 4 Infinity Edges. By the way I lost this game due to being a 3v4 match.To any of you saying that what a shit build on Jinx I'm a Bronze let me build what I want.

body: * So many months ago I was bored and uploaded some videos and this was one of them. I had some fun with stacking Infinity edges when they were 25% Crit ratio with Berserk Boots. But people are stupid and got 2 dislikes over 1 and did not read my crappy description. This was in Team Builder, I am a Bronze and I intend to stay crappy and not really improve at the game, 3v4 against a Teemo and a Morgana which means I can't do crap. Before you say that you shouldn't stack Infinity Edges because they don't stack it just that the PASSIVE DON'T STACK but the Damage and the Crit do plus Jinx's Q passive this was fun. Rant over. Any comments and no this channel is more or less dead, don't really intend to upload videos anymore unless if I managed to learn to edit videos and not upload videos raw.
